name: 艾玛·罗斯
birth_place: 加拿大,艾伯塔省,卡尔加里
introduction: Emma was born in Calgary, Alberta on July 1st, 1999. She discovered acting at the ripe age of four while doing the Nativity play, and hasn't quit since. Primarily establishing her career as an actress in Calgary, Emma has also studied with Broadway Artists Alliance and West End Stage in New York and London respectively.In 2017, she graduated from Bishop Carroll High School and moved to Vancouver, BC to further her career in the arts.
